+/*
+ * SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-or-later
+
+ * Copyright (c) 2020 Intel Corporation
+ * Author: Isaku Yamahata <isaku.yamahata at gmail.com>
+ *                        <isaku.yamahata at intel.com>
+ *
